WEBVTT

00:10.105 --> 00:11.107
What's going on with you, man?

00:11.140 --> 00:12.375
Are you limping?

00:12.407 --> 00:13.943
Uh, no, I've just been working out

00:13.977 --> 00:15.779
on this new exercise bike I got,

00:15.812 --> 00:18.114
- and my glutes are, like, so sore.
- Yeah.

00:18.147 --> 00:19.315
Know what it is?
- Oh.

00:19.349 --> 00:20.983
- Yeah, big-time, big-time.
- Howdy.

00:21.017 --> 00:23.720
- Hi.
- It's... it's very windy today, isn't it?

00:23.752 --> 00:24.720
Yeah.

00:24.754 --> 00:26.790
Oh, man, look at this.

00:26.822 --> 00:28.490
Dog shit.

00:28.523 --> 00:30.559
Did you just step in that on purpose?

00:30.593 --> 00:32.963
Oh, no, I just...
you know, I didn't really see it.

00:33.011 --> 00:34.180
You pointed it out to me!

00:34.214 --> 00:35.815
And then you stepped directly in it.

00:35.849 --> 00:37.684
- Since when do you read?
- What? Nothing. No.

00:38.030 --> 00:39.509
Books are stupid.

00:39.543 --> 00:40.906
I don't. I was just...

00:42.345 --> 00:43.646
It wasn't... like, I didn't time it out.

00:43.680 --> 00:45.783
- I mean, why would I do that?
- I have no idea.

00:45.815 --> 00:48.117
- Why are you still standing in it?
- It was just an accident, man.

00:48.150 --> 00:49.686
People step in dog shit
accidentally all the time.

00:49.720 --> 00:51.888
Is that a lottery scratcher?

00:52.888 --> 00:53.857
Sometimes it's in,

00:53.890 --> 00:55.793
- sometimes it's out.
- Are those mirrors?

00:55.825 --> 00:57.327
- No.
- You creep.

01:05.260 --> 01:06.804
Look out, faggot!

01:08.000 --> 01:14.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:19.830 --> 01:20.932
Holy shit.

01:20.965 --> 01:21.933
God!

01:22.083 --> 01:23.400
Are you okay?

01:24.834 --> 01:26.771
Hey, Frank, what the hell was that?

01:26.804 --> 01:28.906
What? I saved your life.

01:28.938 --> 01:30.206
