because I was just about to do

09:53.065 --> 09:54.910
- a sweet backflip to safety when you...
- Oh, bullshit.

09:54.942 --> 09:56.424
He's never once flipped!

09:56.456 --> 09:57.972
- Here we go.
- I do flips all the time.

09:58.005 --> 09:59.223
- You have never once flipped.
- In the pool?

09:59.257 --> 10:00.738
Which you would not have done

10:00.771 --> 10:03.999
had I not warned you,
thereby saving your life!

10:04.032 --> 10:05.514
That is my ticket.

10:05.548 --> 10:07.260
Oh...

10:07.293 --> 10:09.406
Ridiculous. "Backflip."

10:12.740 --> 10:15.510
<i>There I was, minding my own business,</i>

10:15.680 --> 10:16.765
<i>bird watching.</i>

10:16.798 --> 10:18.056
Beautiful day, isn't it?

10:18.087 --> 10:19.689
It's really gorgeous and...

10:19.941 --> 10:20.965
Are those mirrors?

10:20.997 --> 10:23.047
- No.
- You creep.

10:23.080 --> 10:24.502
He wasn't really bird watching,

10:24.536 --> 10:26.023
he was looking up women's skirts.

10:26.056 --> 10:27.015
- He peeps on women.
- That's his move.

10:27.048 --> 10:28.040
He's disgusting.

10:28.073 --> 10:29.992
Like I said, bird watching.

10:30.025 --> 10:31.679
Not you.

10:31.711 --> 10:35.150
Now, the point is that I said,

10:35.182 --> 10:36.638
"Look out, faggot,"

10:36.671 --> 10:38.588
which were the words
that saved Mac's life.

10:38.621 --> 10:42.227
Thereby, I am entitled to
at least half that ticket.

10:42.260 --> 10:44.575
Well, why did you use the slur

10:44.607 --> 10:46.823
instead of just yelling
your friend's name?

